<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .header {
            background: #EF4444;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }

        .content {
            background: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
        }

        .info-box {
            background: white;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>‚ùå Appointment Canceled</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hi <strong>{{recipientName}}</strong>,</p>
            <p>Unfortunately, your appointment has been canceled by the {{canceledBy}}.</p>

            <div class="info-box">
                <p><strong>üìÖ Date:</strong> {{date}}</p>
                <p><strong>‚è∞ Time:</strong> {{time}}</p>
                <p><strong>üë§ With:</strong> {{otherPartyName}}</p>
                {{#if cancelReason}}
                <p><strong>üìù Reason:</strong> {{cancelReason}}</p>
                {{/if}}
            </div>

            <p>You can book a new appointment at your convenience.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Appointment System - Automated notification</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>